<h2 class="text-center">Agreement</h2>


<p>Taking into account that:</p>
<div style="padding-left: 2em;">
  <p>This agreement is an integral part of the public offer placed on the Internet at http://icoach.io/offer-en/ (hereinafter referred to as the Offer). The Author accepts the Offer fully and unconditionally by signing this agreement.</p>
  <p>This agreement defines the individual conditions for the producer to carry out work to promote the Author. General conditions of work are determined by the Offer.</p>
  <p>This agreement is an integral part of a single agreement formed together with the Offer, the Offer and the Agreement can not be considered separately from each other.</p>
  <p>This agreement expresses a complete agreement between the Parties and replaces all previous oral and written agreements of the parties regarding its subject matter and conditions.</p>
</div>
<p>The parties agreed on the following individual conditions for the implementation of works on promotion:</p>
